Hello, thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides, your favorite bowling alley! My name is Alex. May I have your name, please?

Hi Alex, my name is Jordan.

Thank you, Jordan. How can I assist you with your billing today?

I had a question about my last bill. I think I was charged twice.

I'm sorry to hear that. Let me look into it for you. Could you please provide me with your account number?

Sure, it’s one two three four five.

Thank you. Also, could you confirm the last four digits of your phone number on the account?

Yes, it’s seven eight nine zero.

Great, just a moment while I check your billing records. It seems like there was indeed a duplicate charge. I'll go ahead and refund one of the charges to your account.

That would be great, thank you!

You're welcome, Jordan. Thank you for your patience. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a wonderful day!

Thanks, Alex. You too!
